'''Hykie Berg''' (yavutse 2 Gicurasi 1978), ni umukinnyi wa [[Afurika y’Epfo|filimi Afrika yepfo]] . Azwi cyane ku ruhare rwa 'Darius du Buisson' muri televiziyo ya ''Egoli: Place of Gold'' n'uruhare 'Conrad Bester' mu ikinmico, ''Binnelanders'' . Muri 2011, yatsindiye igihembwe cya kane cyamarushanwa yukuri ''Survivor South Africa''. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 2 Gicurasi 1978 i Pretoria, muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]]. Yize kugeza mu cyiciro cya 8 mu ishuri ryisumbuye rya Die Wilgers aho yatangiye gukoresha ibiyobyabwenge. Hanyuma yize mu 1998. Afite imyaka 19, yabaye umusinzi. Nyuma yaje gukira ibiyobyabwenge  mu bitaro by’indwara zo mu mutwe bya Weskoppies, Cape Town. 

Kuva mu 1997 na 1999, yarangije Impamyabumenyi y’ubucuruzi mu kwamamaza - Umwaka wa kabiri, Kwamamaza / Kwamamaza ibicuruzwa muri kaminuza ya Pretoriya . Hanyuma yarangije impamyabumenyi ya Bachelor muri Dramatic Arts mu buhanzi, imyidagaduro, no gucunga itangazamakuru muri kaminuza ya Stellenbosch hagati ya 1999 na 2002. 

Yashyingiranywe mbere na Melissa Jacobs mu 2013 ariko batandukana muri 2018. <ref>https://www.jacarandafm.com/news/entertainment/binnelanders-star-hykie-berg-confirms-split-we-got-divorced-few-months-ago/</ref> Hanyuma, yasabye inshuti ye yumukobwa Gerridene ku ya 23 kamena 2019 aho amaherezo bashyingiranywe muri Werurwe 2020. <ref>https://www.news24.com/channel/the-juice/news/pics-actor-hykie-berg-ties-the-knot-20200323</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Yatangiye kuri tereviziyo mu rukurikirane rw'urubyiruko ruzwi cyane ''muri Res'' mu 2003. Hanyuma muri 2004, yagize uruhare runini muri serial ''Plek van Meats'' .  Muri 2007, yakinnye bwa mbere muri firime muri ''Ouma se Slim Kind'' . Mu 2004, yinjiye mu bakinnyi ba shampiyona 13 ya ''seri ya tereviziyo Egoli: Place of Gold'' kandi yakinnye nka 'Darius du Buisson' aho yatsindiye igihembo cya Crystal. Yakinnye ibihe bitatu kugeza muri saison 15 muri 2007.

Muri 2018, yabaye umwanditsi aho yasohoye igitabo ''Hykie Berg: Ultimate Survivor'' . Igitabo kivuga ku buzima bwe bw’ibiyobyabwenge ndetse n’urupfu hafi y’umwuga we wo gukina, aho amaherezo abasha kwisubiraho no kugera ku ntsinzi nyuma. <ref>https://www.nb.co.za/en/view-book/?id=9780796321114</ref>

